<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/reset.css"/>
		<script src="js/rem.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
		<script src="js/jquery-2.2.4.min.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>
		<title></title>
		<style type="text/css">
			.pay-success-520-gray{
				position: fixed;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				max-width: 750px;
				min-width: 320px;
				top: 0;
				background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
				/*display: none;*/
			}
			.pay-success-520{
				width: 5.9rem;
				height: 4.8rem;
				background-color: #FFFFFF;
				border-radius: 0.1rem;
				position: absolute;
				top: 50%;
				left: 50%;
				margin-left: -2.95rem;
				margin-top: -2.4rem;
				border-radius: 0.25rem;
			}
			.pay-success-520 .pay-tit{
				height: 1.3rem;
				font-size: 0.36rem;
				line-height: 1.3rem;
				text-align: center;
				background: url(img/tit-bg-520.png) 0 0 no-repeat;
				background-size: 100% 100%;
				color: #FFFFFF;
			}
			.pay-success-520 .pay-tit img{
				display: inline-block;
				width: 0.58rem;
				height: 0.59rem;
				margin-right: 0.2rem;
			}
			.pay-success-520 .text1{
				font-size: 0.32rem;
				color: #666666;
				text-align: center;
				margin-top: 0.5rem;
			}
			.pay-success-520 .text2-shang{
				margin-top: 0.2rem;
			}
			.pay-success-520 .text2-shang,.pay-success-520 .text2-xia{
				font-size: 0.26rem;
				color: #999999;
				text-align: center;
				line-height: 0.36rem;
			}
			.pay-two-btn520{
				display: block;
				width: 100%;
				height: 1rem;
				overflow: hidden;
				position: absolute;
				bottom: 0;
				left: 0;
				font-size: 0.3rem;
				border-top: 0.01rem solid #cccccc;
			}
			.pay-two-btn520 .close,.pay-two-btn520 .pers-center{
				width: 50%;
				display: block;
				float: left;
				text-align: center;
				line-height: 1rem;
			}
			.pay-two-btn520 .close{
				color: #666666;
				border-right: 0.01rem solid #cccccc;
			}
			.pay-two-btn520 .pers-center{
				color: #fb0200;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="pay-success-520-gray">
			<div class="pay-success-520">
				<p class="pay-tit">
					<img src="img/pay-success-logo.png" alt="" />
					支付成功
				</p>
				<p class="text1">您已成功享受5.2折优惠！</p>
				<p class="text2-shang">折扣将以债权金红包形式返还至个人</p>
				<p class="text2-xia">中心，请注意查收！</p>
				<p class="pay-two-btn520">
					<span class="close">关闭</span>
					<a href="###" class="pers-center">个人中心</a>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<script type="text/javascript">
			$('.pay-two-btn520 .close').click(function(){
				$('.pay-success-520-gray').fadeOut();
			});
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
